

---

name: InpatientController
description: The InpatientController is a REST controller that provides endpoints for retrieving user information, interacting with the MRAppClient, and checking the tenant configuration with the FeatureToggleMicroserviceClient.
endpoints:
  - name: hello
    description: Returns a hello message with the provided name, tenant id, user id, tenant name, and user name.
    method: GET
    path: /v1/api/hello
  - name: helloUserInfo
    description: Returns a UserInfoDTO object with the tenant id, user id, tenant name, and user name.
    method: GET
    path: /v1/api/helloUserInfo
  - name: helloFeign
    description: Returns a list of objects from the MRAppClient.
    method: GET
    path: /v1/api/helloFeign
  - name: helloFeatureToggle
    description: Returns a boolean value based on the tenant configuration with the FeatureToggleMicroserviceClient.
    method: GET
    path: /v1/api/helloFeatureToggle